<thead>
<tr>
<th>Voucher</th>
<th>Date</th>
<th>Invoice</th>
<th>Amount in transaction currency debit</th>
<th>Amount in transaction currency credit</th>
<th>Balance</th>
<th>Currency</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Inv-10010</td>
<td>6/25/2015</td>
<td>10010</td>
<td></td>
<td>1,000.00</td>
<td>-1,000.00</td>
<td>USD</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>From the <strong>Vendors</strong> page, April opens the <strong>Settle transactions</strong> page. She can use the <strong>Settle transactions</strong> page to view the dates and amounts of cash discounts. The due date is July 25, and a cash discount of -10.00 is available if the invoice is paid by July 9.</p>
